{"tid":853853,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴名宿：雲格可以給曼聯新開始","createTime":"2018-10-09T02:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T03:50:33.000Z","uid":54373,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"76b69cc1ea895e35fa72a32c350641b075d0396d","tid":853853,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"曼聯領隊摩連奴被炒的說法愈來愈盛，前阿仙奴中場麥臣揚言如果摩佬真的離隊，雲格會是「紅魔鬼」主帥的好人選。<br />\n<br />\n麥臣解釋：「說真的，這不是太壞的主意，你看看雲格做過的事。有他發掘過的潛力之星，你不需要花7、8千萬鎊去買球員。雲格當曼聯主帥不是壞主意，有時你就需要一個新鮮的開始。」"},{"pid":"92d34dd587d775591a5852a035f3d4cd4673c08e","tid":853853,"uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7dd7b1b7d8fb07ff7899cf0e5481d62f2d2c71","tid":853853,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"拎傑斯番黎教都好過雲膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4495d40bf4a92e0fa21cada8a8579574389c572b","tid":853853,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:31:23.000Z","msg":"至少有前四"},{"pid":"6765b6a0c03d6c36a5e51b842bfb34ec229e4eaf","tid":853853,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/photos/arsenal-player-paul-merson-celebrates-during-their-50-league-division-picture-id517980920?s=612x612\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.gettyimages.com%2Fphotos%2Farsenal-player-paul-merson-celebrates-during-their-50-league-division-picture-id517980920%3Fs%3D612x612&h=b786e167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed801fd472b59a1e694924c4ba1485351cfd658b","tid":853853,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"你不需要花